00208 /***********************************************************************
00209    Data structures for open ADF files
00210     in_use: number of times this file has been 'opened'
00211     nlinks : number of linked files opened by this file
00212     links : the list of linked files opened
00213     file_name : name of the open file
00214     open_mode:  The mode the file was opened in.
00215     version_update:  If library file version is greater than
00216        file version, library file version (what-string) is temporarily
00217        stored in this array to update to the file.  The file only
00218        needs its version updated once while open, so don't expect the
00219        version to persist until file closing.  Otherwise, the first
00220        byte in the string is null ('\0').
00221     format : format of the file
00222     os_size : operating system size
00223     link_separator : separator character for links
00224     file: The system-returned file descriptor of an opened file.
00225 ***********************************************************************/
00226
